{{refimprove|date=May 2018}}
XP-Pen is founded in Japan in 2005, it specializes in graphics tablets, pen display monitors, light pads, stylus pens and digital graphical products. In 2008 they established an office in Taiwan. In 2013, XP-Pen Technology Co. was founded in the United States. In 2015 they opened their office in [[Shenzhen]], China. <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.xp-pen.com/about/index/id/16.html|title=xp-pen|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=May 29, 2018}}</ref>
In December 2017, they were invited to [[DreamWorks Animation|DreamWorks]] campus in [[Glendale, California|Glendale]] California.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.xp-pen.com/article/show/id/99.html|title=Visit to DreamWorks Campus-xp-pen|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=May 29, 2018}}</ref> in October 2017, they exhibited in [[Stan Lee]] Comic Con during the Halloween weekend.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.xp-pen.com/article/show/id/100.html|title=XP-Pen Stan Lee Comic Con-xp-pen|last=|first=|date=January 30, 2018|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=May 29, 2018}}</ref> In July 2017, they took part in Los Angeles' 25th [[Anime Expo]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.xp-pen.com/article/show/id/76.html|title=XP-Pen in Anime Expo 2017-xp-pen|last=|first=|date=August 15, 2017|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=May 29, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://id-films.net/v-meet-xp-pen-team-in-anime-expo-VIbCyPgNRPE.html|title=Meet XP-Pen Team in Anime Expo!!!|last=|first=|date=|website=|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=May 29, 2018}}</ref>
